content: I usually call my parents around 7 pm on Sundays. And I meet Chris at 8:30 am on Saturdays. Also, I have lunch with my marketing team colleagues every Wednesday, and I'd like to schedule that in. Oh, and I was thinking of helping my sister with her kids' homework again, so I'll need to block out some time for that. By the way, I helped her last week on Wednesday from 4 pm to 6 pm, and it worked out pretty well.
